name: Adorable plushie Tammy the owl
description:
Hello,
I am an owl called Tammy and i'm a mis-match of colours. I am hand stitched and made out of purple felt and stuffed with cuddly soft polyester with a multi-coloured patchwork back. I have big bright eyes and puffy wings, i'm weighted at the bottom so I sit nice and stable watching the World go by. I measure approx 12cm tall and 12cm wide looking for a nice new home. I'm not suitable for small children due to small parts

name: Lovely kiddies butterfly & star mobile, bright colours, pretty
description: Handmade kiddies butterfly and star mobile made from felt, foam and wool. Brighly coloured, it measures approx 55cm in length, top red and purple flower piece measures 10.5cm diameter. Shapes include large and small butterflies and large and small stars in purple, yellow, orange and red. It has a split ring on top for easy hanging and each string has a little bead on the bottom. Would be an ideal gift for a little girl's room. As this is handmade it is not suitable as a toy due to small parts. Thanks for looking

name: Lovely mini baby bunting for pram, cot, wall
description: New price. Here for sale is a lovely, decorative baby bunting handmade in Cornwall. It has teddy bears and flowers all decorated with sequins, buttons and ribbon. It has 4 'flags' each 10cm tall and 13cm wide, and measures approx in 57cm length. It has a split ring on either end for hanging. Would make a lovely addition to a little girls bedroom, cot, pram etc.
